<TITLE> Aminul, Milon, Faisal get HC bail </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Aug 6 (bdnews24.com)  Former telecommunications minister Aminul Haque, former state minister for education Ehsanul Haque Milon and Faisal Morshed Khan, son of former foreign minister M Morshed Khan, secured bail from the High Court in separate separate cases on Thursday. A High Court bench of justices Abdul Wahab Miah and Abdur Razzak granted one-year interim bail to Aminul in an illegal assets case. The same bench granted Milon six-month anticipatory bail in a case brought against him for not submitting an account of his election expenditure to the Election Commission on time. Another bench of justices Syed Mohammad Dastagir Hossain and Mohammad Rais Uddin granted six-month interim bail to Faisal in an illegal assets case. bdne
